{
  "stem": "27340.2",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Now, you can imagine that 12 and eight-year-old boy was not, uh, going to carry a tremendous amount of equipment.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And by equipment, I mean basically clothes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I remember, for instance, that, uh, my father and I think my mother sat on the suitcase in order to close the thing.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was so chockablock full of clothes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the suitcase of my brother was, of course, somewhat smaller than mine.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because the bastard Nazis at the station at Breslau-- it was all by train-- in fact, demanded that we showed to them that we were able of carrying that suitcase.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] You know, we dragged this thing along the platform.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we passed the test, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so we were off into the train.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "Now, the point to remember here is that my case was exactly like everybody else's.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Parents kissed their children goodbye without knowing ever if they were going to see them again.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "My case was somewhat different, which perhaps I can elaborate on a little later.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "But, uh, the sacrifice that these parents made must have been tremendous.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "At that time, obviously, to me, this was all terrific excitement-- a new country, a train journey.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I had never been on the train for quite such a distance.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Breslau is in eastern Germany, as I mentioned before.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So this went all the way across Germany and all the way across Holland to Hoek van Holland.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Then, we were going to go on a boat-- I'd never been on a boat before-- the ferry from Hoek van Holland to Harwich, and then again into a train.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "So this was terrific excitement.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes, very much so, very much so.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was an adventure, as far as I was concerned.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
